dan pergi ke lantai

00:06:42.817 --> 00:06:45.076
pertama.  Dia ada
di kamar nomor lima.

00:06:45.116 --> 00:06:46.247
Terima kasih.  Ayo.

00:06:49.721 --> 00:06:52.566
Di ruangan manakah Gurinder Bajwa?
